Package eu.wauz.wauzcore.skills.particles

This package contains classes for creating advanced particle effects.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Colors
    A collection of default dye colors.
    ParticleSpawner
    A collection of methods to spawn particles in different shapes and animations.
    SkillParticle
    A template for a particle, that can be spawned manually or by a particle spawner.
